rows.label: campfev11_360_100_msg0001
rows.name:
We should probably think about making
contact with the resistance fairly soon.

rows.label: campfev11_360_100_msg0002
rows.name:
You're right...
They're waiting for us.

rows.label: campfev11_360_100_msg0003
rows.name:
Laura.. We shouldn't be wasting time
like this. We need to head straight to
Aletta, no diversions.

rows.label: campfev11_360_100_msg0005
rows.name:
I just need a moment to get into
the right frame of mind...

rows.label: campfev11_360_100_msg0006
rows.name:
I didn't know there was a "right
frame of mind" for this!
